title: Watch Goldfrapp Lead a Desert Ritual in New “Anymore” Video
text: Goldfrapp have shared the video for “Anymore” from their new album Silver Eye , via Dazed . In the Mary Calderwell-produced clip, filmed in Fuerteventura, Alison Goldfrapp leads a troupe of dancers in a mysterious desert ritual. Check it out below. Artists In This Story
